## Supabase Free vs Paid (Relevant for Support)
| Feature | Free | Pro ($25/mo) |
|---|---|---|
| Project pausing | After 7 days inactivity | Never |
| DB storage | 500MB | 8GB |
| File storage | 1GB | 100GB |
| Bandwidth | 5GB/month | 250GB/month |
| Edge function calls | 500K/month | 2M+/month |

**Note**: Supabase Pro ($25/mo) is separate from the Rocket plan. It eliminates project pausing — the #1 cause of "app randomly broke" issues.

