## Supabase Diagnostic Checklist
- [ ] Project active at supabase.com (not paused)?
- [ ] All migration scripts pushed and showing "Applied"?
- [ ] Redirect URLs include production domain AND localhost?
- [ ] RLS enabled AND correct policies set on all tables?
- [ ] Auth providers enabled + OAuth credentials configured?
- [ ] Storage bucket type correct (public vs private)?
- [ ] Edge functions deployed if used?
- [ ] Env variables correct in production (Netlify)?

