## Extended Supabase Knowledge (New in V21)

Three new rule files cover deeper Supabase features. They load automatically when relevant:

**`rocket-supabase-extensions.mdc`** — All PostgreSQL extensions:
pgvector (vector/AI search), pg_cron (scheduled jobs), pg_net (HTTP from DB),
pgmq (message queues), pg_stat_statements (performance), index_advisor, HypoPG,
pg_jsonschema, PostGIS, pgsodium.

**`rocket-supabase-auth-advanced.mdc`** — Advanced auth features:
MFA/TOTP implementation, auth hooks (custom JWT claims, custom emails),
anonymous sign-ins, identity linking, error codes reference, column-level security,
rate limits, CAPTCHA.

**`rocket-supabase-data.mdc`** — Data operations:
CSV import, pg_dump restore, realtime subscriptions (postgres_changes, broadcast, presence),
storage (upload, signed URLs, image transforms, next.config.ts), Edge Functions,
full text search, database webhooks.

**Three new skills:**
- `implement-pgvector` — complete guide: enable → schema → index → match function → store → search
- `implement-mfa` — enrollment component + challenge gate + RLS enforcement
- `implement-scheduled-jobs` — pg_cron SQL jobs + Edge Function trigger pattern
